REQUIREMENTS:
	Eigen library (http://eigen.tuxfamily.org/)
		Modify DIR1 to point to the directory where the Eigen library is installed
	FFTW library (version 3 or greater)
INSTRUCTIONS:
	raman_thole.exe
		computes raman spectrum from molecular dynamics simulation
		to build: "make raman"
	ir_qeq.exe
		computes ir spectrum from molecular dynamics simulation
		to build: "make ir"
	nlo_atom.exe
		computes SFG spectrum from molecular dynamics simulation
		to build: "make nlo"

# qatom
